reuse-annotate  [alias: pipx run reuse annotate --year 2023 --copyright 'Ruben Laguna <ruben.laguna@gmail.com>' --license GPL-3.0-or-later]

Add REUSE-compliant SPDX copyright/license headers to the given
files using the user's standard copyright and GPL-3.0-or-later
license. Pass file paths as arguments.
